{"tid":1197771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國民運歷史: 勇武派與和平派, 互相尊重各有各做","createTime":"2019-06-10T05:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T11:36:31.000Z","uid":134071,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"594a93c9b85e352066620dab06fc9c13adb84408","tid":1197771,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/photos/a.155136541681491/565450227316785/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk%2Fphotos%2Fa.155136541681491%2F565450227316785%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=2510f23f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/photos/a.155136541681491/565450227316785/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\nGoodbye HK, Hello UK<br />\n4小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【割蓆、篤灰、自套光環】<br />\n<br />\n掌聲比自己好容易，指出他人錯處亦都唔難<br />\n<br />\n五六十年代美國黑人民權運動，好多人會比較熟識「和理非」嘅國際級代言人物馬丁路德金（Martin Luther King Jr. ）。不過有時會忽略咗同期激進派領袖，主張「勇武」抗爭嘅Malcolm X。身處一樣咁不公義同扭曲嘅環境同時空，講目標難行，兩個都坐過監然後先後都被刺殺，夠難未？講抗爭手法極端，一個和理非到打不還手，另一個激到黑白二元對立以暴易暴，夠極端未？<br />\n<br />\n雖然Malcolm X覺得和理非行為軟弱，最多語言上單單打打，但有無响和平示威期間搞事？無。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Dr. King wants the same thing I want. Freedom.&rdquo; &mdash; Malcolm X<br />\n<br />\n馬丁路德金從來不認同武力抗爭，亦感到「勇武」有時會拉自己後腳，但係有無割蓆、篤灰或者自套光環？亦都無。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;While we did not always see eye to eye on methods to solve the race problem, I always had a deep affection for Malcolm and felt that he had a great ability to put his finger on the existence and root of the problem..&rdquo; &mdash; Martin Luther King Jr.<br />\n<br />\n當大家都明白終極目標係乜，共同敵人係邊個，互相尊重各有各做，係咪咁難？"},{"pid":"ad112835b2cfd23e4c94fb7e14793fcfd7548f32","tid":1197771,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe75e0c6f31aa71f4a3b29d1610a56ffc771a18","tid":1197771,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"推推歷史"},{"pid":"f9cca4617e6ff8447ac9abd36a2d18f405e34bcf","tid":1197771,"uid":45536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n雖然兩邊都無個似樣嘅leader"},{"pid":"e51bd2cbd091bcc234d6eb4692219b0c0bfe3384","tid":1197771,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d77cc10a4d16af0149151bb34d68051f637522d","tid":1197771,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479e6ab02ca85a080cbaa036f15a4e52ab0efe16","tid":1197771,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5db96d0a8d0e7a1b80aedaf5ded72b0451ef3584","tid":1197771,"uid":28641,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"各有各做<br />\n而家100萬人做既野<br />\n仲少過魚蛋一千人做既野<br />\n醒下啦<br />\n你地琴日遊行係完全無幫到香港任何野<br />\n唔好再打飛機啦<br />\n垃圾華人奴隸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841c9e9d8cacd2707cdc1772092e9c5d04239454","tid":1197771,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"連登仔識睇歷史 就唔會話雨傘過後已經死心唔出口弓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d43d5e09c3cce31f7d8add9c49045e008135486","tid":1197771,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0014a4ac88d1ff6524595514fe7fd6f974f6a2c","tid":1197771,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re